Tips for Successful Completion:

Start with authentication first.
Build post creation and feed functionality.
Add likes and comments.
Implement friend requests.
Create REST APIs using DRF.
Test every module.
Deploy early on Render or Railway.
Keep documentation updated.
Push code regularly to GitHub.
Use Git branches for new features.

